description: Rocko’s Ice Cream Tacos serves handcrafted ice cream tacos and other frozen treats (frozen bananas, s’more tacos, etc.) All desserts are made using organic and locally sourced ingredients, and customized using liquid nitrogen to flash freeze on the spot. Our ice cream tacos consist of waffle cone tacos shells filled with an ice cream of choice, dipped into a chocolate or peanut butter dip and rolled in toppings.  A delicious treat for both kids and kids at heart!  We serve at festivals, parties, weddings, and corporate events.
name: Rocko's Ice Cream Tacos
